'''Warden Squadron''' was one of the three [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wing]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Squadron/Legends|squadrons]] that made up [[Defender Wing]] under the command of [[General/Legends|General]] [[Horton Salm/Legends|Horton Salm]]. The other two were [[Guardian Squadron|Guardian]] and [[Champion Squadron|Champion]] Squadrons.

==History==
During the final stages of a successful raid on the [[Rachuk sector/Legends|Rachuk Sector]] headquarters of the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] located on [[Vladet]], Warden Squadron, using targeting data provided by [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]] of [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]], destroyed the [[Lancer-class frigate/Legends|''Lancer''-class frigate]] [[Ravager (Lancer-class)|''Ravager'']]. The unit would later participate in the taking of [[Yag-prime]] during the crisis surrounding the release of the [[Krytos virus]].

At some point later in the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], Guardian Squadron's Y-wings were updated to [[BTL-S8 K-wing assault starfighter]]s.

